      "acceptedAnswer":{
        "@type":"Answer",
        "text":"Yes. PB Fulfill supports fulfillment from both US East Coast and West Coast warehouses. These warehouses provide inventory storage, local delivery, and return handling to help ecommerce businesses reduce shipping times and improve customer satisfaction."
