      "@type":"Question",
      "name":"Can unused inventory be refunded?",
      "acceptedAnswer":{
        "@type":"Answer",
        "text":"PB Fulfill first confirms with the manufacturer whether returns are accepted. If the factory does not accept returns, unused inventory cannot be refunded. Customers are encouraged to stock inventory based on recent sales trends."
      }
